I was debating about your repro handle... I use the sliding door for all
entrys into and out of the van and it is my daily driver so the sliding
door gets a lot of abuse.  the plastic handles don't last very long...so
some years ago I made one out of Aluminum bar stock, not factory looking,
left it bare metal but it has held up for 8-9 years so far...

